---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Grants - Antarctica DAO">
	<h1>Antarctica DAO Grants Program</h1>
	
	<section>
		<h2>Empowering Farcaster Ecosystem Development</h2>
		<p>The Antarctica DAO Grants Program aims to support and accelerate the growth of the Farcaster ecosystem by providing funding and resources to promising projects, developers, and initiatives.</p>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Grant Categories</h2>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Protocol Development:</strong> Improvements and extensions to the core Farcaster protocol</li>
			<li><strong>Client Applications:</strong> Innovative Farcaster clients and user interfaces</li>
			<li><strong>Infrastructure:</strong> Tools and services that enhance the Farcaster network</li>
			<li><strong>Integrations:</strong> Projects that connect Farcaster with other Web3 protocols or traditional platforms</li>
			<li><strong>Community and Education:</strong> Initiatives that grow and educate the Farcaster community</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Grant Sizes</h2>
		<p>We offer grants in various sizes to accommodate different project scopes:</p>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Micro Grants:</strong> Up to $5,000 for small projects or prototypes</li>
			<li><strong>Small Grants:</strong> $5,000 - $25,000 for more substantial projects</li>
			<li><strong>Large Grants:</strong> $25,000 - $100,000 for significant contributions to the ecosystem</li>
			<li><strong>Custom Grants:</strong> For exceptional projects that require more substantial funding</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Application Process</h2>
		<ol>
			<li><strong>Initial Proposal:</strong> Submit a brief overview of your project idea</li>
			<li><strong>Review:</strong> Our team will review your proposal and provide feedback</li>
			<li><strong>Detailed Application:</strong> If invited, submit a comprehensive grant application</li>
			<li><strong>Evaluation:</strong> The Antarctica DAO community will evaluate and vote on your application</li>
			<li><strong>Decision:</strong> Successful applicants will be notified and receive funding</li>
			<li><strong>Milestone Tracking:</strong> Regular check-ins and progress reports throughout the grant period</li>
		</ol>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Evaluation Criteria</h2>
		<p>We assess grant applications based on the following criteria:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Alignment with Farcaster's vision and principles</li>
			<li>Potential impact on the Farcaster ecosystem</li>
			<li>Technical feasibility and team expertise</li>
			<li>Originality and innovation</li>
			<li>Open-source commitment</li>
			<li>Sustainability and long-term viability</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Apply for a Grant</h2>
		<p>Ready to contribute to the Farcaster ecosystem? We encourage you to apply for a grant and bring your ideas to life!</p>
		<a href="#" class="cta-button">Submit a Grant Proposal</a>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	section {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	ul, ol {
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}
	.cta-button {
		display: inline-block;
		background-color: var(--accent-color);
		color: var(--background-color);
		padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 5px;
		font-weight: bold;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
	}
	.cta-button:hover {
		background-color: var(--text-color);
	}
</style>